snippet.title: Monsta Tapwar Trailer: The Origins of Tapwar
snippet.description:
Monsta Tapwar is the first prodigy child of Monsta Infinite's various contributions to the gaming and cryptocurrency industry. Combining the best of competitive online gaming and Decentralised finance, Monsta Infinite aims to take over the industry and build a brighter, more sustainable future for all users to benefit.
